text: Van Dyke's salamander (Plethodon vandykei) is a species of salamanders. They are part of the family Plethodontidae. These salamanders have been used in research studies. == Subspecies == *Washington Salamander, Plethodon vandykei vandykei *Coeur D'Alene Salamander, Plethodon vandykei idahoensis ==References== == Other websites == * Pictures *Distribution Map Category:Salamanders
title: Van Dyke's salamander
